message.entry: The input image is already binary.
Truecolor RGB image must be an M-by-N-by-3 array.
Input colormap must be an M-by-3 matrix.
Colormap intensities must be between 0 and 1.
Threshold luminance must be a non-negative number between 0 and 1.
Code generation is not supported. Use IMQUANTIZE instead.
